metadata.name: pepe leading the ppl
metadata.description:
As the residents of Keksaw banded together for the Kekrising, little did they know they were part of a line of proud beings who also worked in unison to fight against the oppressive powers at be.

In fact, there are relics in time, such as this one, capturing the moments of these brave beings battling for culture.

These relics contain symbols of hope, belief, and spirit in the fight for art, memes, and culture.  The relics create a consistent lineage of those beings willing to stand for the culture. 

The bravery of those beings stands eternal connected from the past through the present
